hopobject.body: Have you got a telephone directory? maxmanroe paspor Fitch modelled the credit risk of the portfolio using its criteria for the analysis of public-sector pools published in January 2013. In a 'AA-' scenario, Fitch calculated a stressed credit loss of 1.4%, whereby the stressed defaults and recoveries are 1.8% and 21.1%, respectively. In this scenario, the Federal Republic of Germany (AAA/Stable/F1 ) is not assumed to default.
